{"tid":621183,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩有個C9係M記用部點餐機用成十分鐘","createTime":"2018-04-08T06:09:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-10T09:55:43.000Z","uid":33359,"like":64,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"258ebff4f744eb2d232e3f31a76a745185e4e74b","tid":621183,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T06:09:28.000Z","msg":"一入M記,3部機都有人<br />\n第一部係個老母帶個女<br />\n第二部係3個中學雞,一路禁一路玩緊王者榮耀<br />\n第三部係個C9帶住個仔<br />\n<br />\n權衡利弊之後我簡左企係第三部後面,但係等左2分鐘之後開始心感不妙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為條八婆係逐個逐個MENU禁入去睇有咩岩食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我即時一個抽身走去排有M記仔既COUNTER<br />\n<br />\n到我比完錢,拎埋外賣準備走人個陣<br />\n第三部機個八婆仲未買完,見佢個到已經簡左4,5個ITEMS<br />\n<br />\n之後我直接行去佢面前,乜聲都唔出,係部機到禁&quot;取消訂單&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個八婆首先呆左一呆,幾秒之後先大叫&quot;你做乜阿&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就頭也不回咁走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88a347cc34ffda177c163df7075f7044cf2409ba","tid":621183,"uid":129942,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T06:11:57.000Z","msg":"無圖你話你對住個師奶打飛機都得㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"509ceb383f84e58145d5b281db63e39f6c4161c9","tid":621183,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88a347cc34ffda177c163df7075f7044cf2409ba","tid":621183,"uid":129942,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T06:11:57.000Z","msg":"無圖你話你對住個師奶打飛機都得㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T06:41:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c528ab5f4e4b45621d15cddf51dc61e06bbbe25a","tid":621183,"uid":19005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T08:48:19.000Z","msg":"直接去職員點餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" clas